    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "body": "一个用 Rust 编写的极快的 Python 包和项目管理工具"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "使用独立安装程序安装 - macOS or Linux",
      "body": "```sh\ncurl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Windows",
      "body": "%60%60%60sh%0Apowershell%20-ExecutionPolicy%20ByPass%20-c%20%22irm%20https%3A%2F%2Fastral.sh%2Fuv%2Finstall.ps1%20%7C%20iex%22%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "通过PyPI",
      "body": "```sh\n# pip\npip install uv\n```\n\n```sh\n# pipx\npipx install uv\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-4",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "创建新项目",
      "body": "```sh\n# 创建一个目录作为项目的根目录\nuv init project_name\n```\n\n```sh\n# 将当前目录作为项目的根目录\nuv init\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-5",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "项目的结构",
      "body": "```sh\n.\n├── .venv/           # 虚拟环境目录\n│   ├── bin/         # 可执行文件\n│   ├── lib/         # 安装的库\n│   └── pyvenv.cfg   # 虚拟环境配置\n├── .python-version  # 指定 Python 版本\n├── README.md        # 项目说明文档\n├── main.py          # 主程序入口\n├── pyproject.toml   # 项目配置与依赖声明\n└── uv.lock          # 依赖锁定文件（自动生成）\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-6",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "管理项目依赖 - 添加依赖",
      "body": "```sh\nuv add requests\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-7",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%88%96%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E6%9D%A5%E6%BA%90",
      "body": "%60%60%60sh%0A%23%20%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%0Auv%20add%20'requests%3D%3D2.28.1'%0A%0A%23%20%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E6%9D%A5%E6%BA%90%0Auv%20add%20git%2Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fpsf%2Frequests%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-8",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "从`requirements.txt`迁移",
      "body": "```sh\nuv add -r requirements.txt\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-9",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "删除一个包",
      "body": "```sh\nuv remove requests\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-10",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "升级一个包",
      "body": "```sh\nuv lock --upgrade-package requests\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-11",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "运行脚本",
      "body": "指定脚本运行\n\n```sh\nuv run main.py\n```\n\n指定Python版本运行\n\n```sh\nuv run --python 3.10 main.py\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-15",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "构建项目",
      "body": "```sh\nuv build\n```\n\n构建结果存储在`dist`目录下"
    }
  ],
